New Features
- 🙈 Updated .gitignore to omit `.env` files
- ➕ Added the `jekyll-github-metadata` gem
- ✨ Introduced `sidebar.featured` and `sidebar.recent_posts` parameters
- 🚚 Renamed the site-level parameter from `disqus-amp-baseurl` to `disqus_amp_baseurl`
  to enable/disable displaying Featured and Recent posts in sidebar, respectively

Improvements
- 🔥 Removed chris's author data from _config.yml
- 📝 Added tags to sample posts

Removed/Deprecated
- 🔥 Dropped the site-level parameter `isSubdirectory`
